        <title>Manifold Absolute Pressure (MAP) Sensor</title>
        <figure id="f2650211009" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figH09/H09006.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"/>
            <caption>MAP sensor</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>The MAP sensor, a variable capacitance sensor, detects intake manifold boost pressure.</para>
        <para>The MAP signal is monitored by the ECM for EGR valve, VGT, and engine fueling calculations.</para>
        <para>The MAP sensor is installed in the intake manifold left of the MAT sensor.</para>
    </svcproc>
